# {{CREATOR_NAME}} Brand — Visual Spec (TEMPLATE)

**Status: TEMPLATE.** Fork this file and fill in your own palette, type, and texture rules. This is the single source of truth for your content-brand visual identity. All archetype `STYLE_DECON.md` guides defer to this doc for color, type, and grain treatments. Archetype guides own *format and grammar*; this doc owns *brand*.

If a future style guide's "Brand Adaptation" section conflicts with anything here, this file wins.

