## 0 · The brand essence in one line

**[Your brand essence — one sentence.]**

Examples to draw from:
- "Sage green, warm cream, classical serifs, naturally-graded faces. Premium-but-approachable. Editorial-but-modern."
- "Cobalt + neon yellow, geometric sans, high-contrast monochrome speaker. Confident-but-loud. Tech-startup-but-not-corporate."
- "Cream paper + ink, italic serif, hand-drawn flourishes. Editorial-but-warm. Considered-but-not-precious."

Pick a register. Commit to it. Every visual choice downstream serves it.

